room_title: Escape room "The Incident" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: Seven of us had an excellent time in "The Incident". Very challenging, and - yes - we needed a bit of guidance. Really imaginative and a very fun night out. Thanks!

room_title: Escape room "The Incident" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: My friends and I went here to relax, and we had a blast! The staff was friendly, and really made the whole experience that much more fun! We did The Incident, and it was a tough room but not so tough that it was impossible. It challenged us, and that's what we wanted. I will definitely be going again!
